---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="The future of doctoral learning" description="A research environment for working scholars — flexible doctoral programmes, world-class supervision, and industry-connected innovation.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex flex-col justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden" id="story">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-white pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-200/40 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full relative z-10">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left: text -->
        <div>
          <p class="section-label mb-6">Doctoral College UK</p>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 text-gray-900">
            Shaping the future of doctoral <em class="italic font-light text-blue-600 not-italic">learning</em>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-light max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            A research environment for working scholars — flexible doctoral programmes, world-class supervision, and industry-connected innovation.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/programmes/" class="btn-primary text-base px-7 py-3">Explore Programmes</a>
            <button onclick="document.getElementById('story-modal').classList.remove('hidden')" class="btn-outline text-base px-7 py-3">Our Story</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right: image -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block">
          <img
            src="/Student - PC - Image.jpg"
            alt="Doctoral researcher at work"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover max-h-[520px]"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Modal -->
  <div id="story-modal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 z-[200] flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm" onclick="if(event.target===this)this.classList.add('hidden')">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-2xl w-full overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="bg-[#1e3a6e] px-8 py-6 flex items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <img src="/logo.png" alt="Doctoral College UK" class="h-10 w-auto brightness-0 invert" />
        </div>
        <button onclick="document.getElementById('story-modal').classList.add('hidden')" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white text-2xl leading-none">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="px-8 py-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-accent font-medium text-sm mb-6">Shaping the future of doctoral learning</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-blue-100">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e3a6e]">2020</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Founded with a single conviction: that the most important research questions are held by practitioners already working in the field.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-blue-100">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e3a6e]">40+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Doctoral candidates across business, education, health, and public service — all working professionals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-blue-100">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e3a6e]">10+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Countries represented in our researcher community, spanning the UK, Middle East, Africa, and beyond.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-blue-100">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e3a6e]">97%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Candidate satisfaction — built on rigorous supervision, flexible delivery, and genuine academic community.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Doctoral College UK was established to serve a generation of senior professionals who want to generate original knowledge from within their practice. We offer flexible doctoral programmes, world-class supervision, and a research environment built around the realities of professional life.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
          <a href="/about/" class="btn-primary text-sm">Learn More About Us</a>
          <a href="/apply/" class="btn-outline text-sm">Apply Now</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="border-y border-border bg-surface" id="stats">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold counter text-gray-900" data-target="40" data-suffix="+">0+</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-2">PhDs</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold counter text-gray-900" data-target="10" data-suffix="+">0+</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-2">Countries</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold counter text-gray-900" data-target="97" data-suffix="%">0%</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-2">Satisfaction</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold counter text-gray-900" data-target="12" data-suffix="">0</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-2">Research Themes</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <p class="section-label mb-3">What We Do</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Three pillars define how DCUK advances doctoral education.</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
      <a href="/programmes/" class="card group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/><path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Doctoral Programmes</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed">Flexible pathways from Access to Doctorate through PhD, DBA, and EdD — designed for working researchers.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-accent mt-4">Learn more →</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/research/strategy/" class="card group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Research &amp; Innovation</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed">Twelve themed research groups producing industry-facing publications and commissioned case studies.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-accent mt-4">Learn more →</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/symposium/" class="card group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Events &amp; Community</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed">Our annual Symposium, supervisor workshops, and researcher seminars throughout the year.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-accent mt-4">Learn more →</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Programmes -->
  <section class="border-t border-border bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-12">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label mb-3">Featured Programmes</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Flexible doctoral and training pathways.</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/programmes/" class="text-sm text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors hidden md:block">View all →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

        <a href="/programmes/dba/" class="card group flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Blended</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Doctor of Business Administration (DBA)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed flex-1">A practice-based doctorate for senior professionals applying research to their organisations.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4">Fees £10,000 <span class="text-accent ml-2">Explore →</span></p>
        </a>

        <a href="/programmes/edd/" class="card group flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Online</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Doctor of Education (EdD)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed flex-1">A professional doctorate for educators and educational leaders.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4">Fees £10,000 <span class="text-accent ml-2">Explore →</span></p>
        </a>

        <a href="/programmes/online-phd/" class="card group flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Online</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Doctor of Philosophy (PhD)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed flex-1">A flexible doctoral pathway for working professionals, fully online with expert supervision.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4">Fees £10,000 <span class="text-accent ml-2">Explore →</span></p>
        </a>

        <a href="/programmes/research-training/" class="card group flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="tag tag-training">Training</span>
            <span class="tag tag-training">Modular</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Research Training Programme</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed flex-1">Methodology, analytics, and scholarly-writing modules for researchers at any stage of their career.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4">£600 per Unit <span class="text-accent ml-2">Explore →</span></p>
        </a>

        <a href="/programmes/mphil/" class="card group flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
            <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Flexible</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Extended Advanced Diploma (SCQF)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed flex-1">A post graduate qualification with SCQF credit, ideal as a stepping-stone to PhD or as a standalone qualification.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4">Fees £10,000 <span class="text-accent ml-2">Explore →</span></p>
        </a>

        <a href="/programmes/supervisor-development/" class="card group flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="tag tag-training">Training</span>
            <span class="tag tag-training">Modular</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Supervisor Development Programme</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light leading-relaxed flex-1">Training and CPD for new and experienced doctoral supervisors.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4">Fees £1,200 <span class="text-accent ml-2">Explore →</span></p>
        </a>

      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 text-center md:hidden">
        <a href="/programmes/" class="btn-outline">View all programmes</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- News + Events -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
    <!-- News -->
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-8">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label mb-2">Latest News &amp; Insights</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Fresh thinking from our team.</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/news/" class="text-sm text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">View all →</a>
      </div>
      <ol class="space-y-6">
        <li>
          <a href="/news/director-dispatch-research-worth-doing/" class="flex gap-5 group">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors shrink-0 w-8">1</span>
            <div>
              <div class="flex gap-2 items-center mb-1">
                <span class="text-xs text-muted">Apr 2026</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-muted">·</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-accent">Director's Dispatch</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-medium group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">What management research is actually worth doing in 2026</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-1">By Prof. Stanley Oliver</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/news/executive-research-emerging-trends/" class="flex gap-5 group">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors shrink-0 w-8">2</span>
            <div>
              <div class="flex gap-2 items-center mb-1">
                <span class="text-xs text-muted">Apr 2026</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-muted">·</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-accent">Insights</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-medium group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Executive Research: Emerging Trends Shaping Doctoral Inquiry in 2026</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-1">By Dr Zahra Salimi</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/news/emerging-management-research-areas/" class="flex gap-5 group">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors shrink-0 w-8">3</span>
            <div>
              <div class="flex gap-2 items-center mb-1">
                <span class="text-xs text-muted">Apr 2026</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-muted">·</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-accent">Research</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-medium group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Seven Emerging Management Research Areas Our Supervisors Are Watching</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-1">By Dr Elizabeth Blower</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <!-- Events -->
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-8">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label mb-2">Upcoming Events</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Join us this year.</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/symposium/" class="text-sm text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">View all →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div class="card">
          <p class="text-xs text-accent font-medium mb-2">5 September 2026</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Supervisor Development Workshop</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-light mb-3">Workshop · Fully Online</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light">Intensive one-day workshop for new doctoral supervisors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="text-xs text-accent font-medium mb-2">19 September 2026</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Research Methods Webinar Series</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-light mb-3">Webinar · Fully Online</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light">Monthly webinars on qualitative and quantitative methods.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="text-xs text-accent font-medium mb-2">27–29 October 2026</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Annual Doctoral Symposium 2026</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-light mb-3">Symposium · Online &amp; Newcastle upon Tyne</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light">Three days of keynotes, panels, and workshops for doctoral researchers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Supervisors -->
  <section class="border-t border-border bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-12">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label mb-3">Meet the supervisors</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold max-w-lg text-gray-900">Supervision is the single biggest determinant of a good doctorate.</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/supervisors/" class="text-sm text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors hidden md:block">Browse all supervisors →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">

        <a href="/supervisors/stanley-oliver/" class="card group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">SO</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Prof. Stanley Oliver</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-1">Principal, Doctoral College UK</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-3">mixed · 8 researchers</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent mt-3">Read profile →</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/supervisors/zahra-salimi/" class="card group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-violet-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-violet-600 mb-4">ZS</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Dr. Zahra Salimi</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-1">Academic Lead for Research & Enterprise</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-3">mixed · 8 researchers</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent mt-3">Read profile →</p>
        </a>

<a href="/supervisors/liz-blower/" class="card group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-teal-600 mb-4">LB</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Dr. Liz Blower</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-1">Academic Lead for Operations</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-3">qualitative · 8 researchers</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent mt-3">Read profile →</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/supervisors/adjunct-faculty/" class="card group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-gray-600 mb-4">AF</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Adjunct Faculty</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mt-1">Experienced Supervisors</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-3">mixed · 20+ researchers</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent mt-3">Read profile →</p>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    <div class="card text-center">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Apply</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mb-5">Begin your doctoral journey with a flexible pathway built for working researchers.</p>
      <a href="/apply/" class="btn-primary">Start Application</a>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Partner</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mb-5">Collaborate on research, consultancy, and supervisor training with the DCUK network.</p>
      <a href="/research/consultancy/" class="btn-outline">Explore Partnerships</a>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Attend</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mb-5">Join the annual Symposium, researcher seminars, and supervisor workshops.</p>
      <a href="/symposium/" class="btn-outline">See Events</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
